  "apple-macbook-air-m2-chip-midnight-laptop-mly33hn-a-2022-8gb-ram-256-gb-ssd-13-6-inch-34-46-cm-display-8-core-cpu-8-core-gpu-macos": { highlights: ["Features of Apple MacBook Air M2 Chip Midnight Laptop MLY33HN/A (2022)", "Magic Keyboard: Let your fingers fly", "Comfortable and quiet, Magic Keyboard now has a full-height function key row for quick access to favourite controls and shortcuts. Touch ID makes it easy to unlock your Mac and enter passwords — all at the touch of a finger. And with the larger Force Touch trackpad, there’s even more space to work with precision.", "Connectivity: Keep plugging away", "The quick-release MagSafe power connector easily attaches — and detaches — with magnets, preventing any unintended flights. Two Thunderbolt ports let you connect and power high-speed accessories. You can also connect up to a 6K display. And the headphone jack supports high‑impedance headphones."], specs: [["BRAND", "Apple"], ["MODEL NAME", "MLY33HN/A"], ["SERIES", "MacBook Air M2 (2022)"], ["COLOR", "Midnight"], ["OS", "MacOS"], ["SSD CAPACITY", "256GB SSD"], ["RAM", "8GB unified memory"], ["CHIP", "Apple M2 Chip"], ["Display", "Liquid Retina Display"], ["Wi-Fi", "802.11ax Wi-Fi 6 wireless networking"], ["Bluetooth", "Bluetooth 5.0 wireless technology"], ["Camera", "1080p FaceTime HD camera"], ["Weight", "1.24 kg"], ["Battery And Power", "Up to 18 hours Apple TV app movie playback, Up to 15 hours wireless web, 52.6-watt?hour lithium?polymer battery, 30W USB-C Power Adapter (included with M2 with 8-core GPU)"], ["In The Box", "MacBook Air, 30W USB-C Power Adapter (M2 with 8-core GPU), USB-C to MagSafe 3 Cable (2 meters)"]], overview: "Magic Keyboard: Let your fingers fly" },
