  "lenovo-laptop-bag-15-6-inch-backpack-black-red": { highlights: ["Compatible with 15 inch laptops and below", "Designed from the inside out to offer reliable protection", "Has two compartments and one side pocket", "Includes a customized notebook cradle and workstation section"], specs: [["Brand", "Lenovo"], ["Series", "GX40H34821"], ["Colour", "Black"], ["Standing screen display size", "15.6-inch"], ["Product Dimensions", "45.5 x 19 x 32.5 cm"], ["Manufacturer", "Lenovo"], ["Country of Origin", "China"], ["Item Weight", "‎660 g"]], overview: "The Lenovo Laptop Bag 15.6 Inch Backpack Black Red is the perfect choice for anyone looking for a stylish, yet functional laptop bag. Not only is it sleek and fashionable, but it is also designed with comfort in mind. It features adjustable straps and breathable mesh fabric, so you can stay comfortable while carrying your laptop. Plus, it has plenty of pockets to store all your devices and accessories. Best of all, the Lenovo original laptop bag comes at an unbeatable price! Whether you&#8217;re a student or a professional, this laptop bag is the perfect choice for any laptop user. With its stylish design and comfortable features, it&#8217;s the perfect combination of form and function. So don&#8217;t wait – get your Lenovo laptop bag today and start carrying your laptop in style!" },
