  "asus-rog-backpack": { highlights: ["About this item", "Stylish, gaming-inspired design with the cyber-text pattern and ROG Logo. Material : Polyester", "Quick-access exterior pocket for your essential accessories", "Generous 16L interior for easy transport of an up 15.6-inch laptop", "It also features Ghost chain for better security, Large air mesh back &amp;amp; Luggage strap"], specs: [["Brand", "ASUS"], ["Model", "ROG Backpack BP1501G"], ["Color", "Black"], ["Category", "Backpack"], ["Feature", "Water-Repellent, Lightweight"], ["Dimensions", "43.00 x 30.00 x 14.50 cm"], ["NB Compartment Size", "38.40 x 26.20 x 3.00 cm"], ["Weight", "0.48 kg"], ["Material", "Polyester, Reversed Polyester"]], overview: "The Asus ROG Backpack BP1501 is a high-end gaming backpack designed for gamers who are always on the move. It features a spacious interior that can accommodate laptops up to 15.6 inches in size, making it an ideal choice for gamers who need to bring their gaming machines with them wherever they go. The backpack is made from high-quality materials that are both durable and water-resistant, ensuring that your laptop and other gaming equipment will be protected from the elements." },
  "zebronics-zeb-u1200-ups": { highlights: ["About this item", "Zebronics 1000va UPS", "Genretor compatible", "overload proctection", "micro controller based", "sleep mode charging", "LED indicator", "dual battery"], specs: [["Brand", "Zebronics"], ["Model Number", "ZEB-U1200"], ["Special Features", "‎600VA/360W, COLD START"], ["Colour", "Black"], ["Product Dimensions", "32 x 13 x 18.2 cm"], ["Batteries", "‎1 Lithium Metal batteries required. (included)"], ["Input Voltage", "140 V"], ["Input Frequency", "60/50 Hz"], ["Output Voltage", "1000 V"], ["Output Frequency", "60 Hz or 50 Hz ±1 Hz"], ["Efficiency", "90 %"], ["Country of Origin", "India"]], overview: "The Zebronics Zeb U1200 UPS is a highly reliable and efficient power backup solution for your devices. It is designed to protect your devices from power surges, spikes, and outages, ensuring that your work stays uninterrupted even during power cuts. This UPS comes with an input voltage range of 140V – 300V, providing a stable output voltage of 230V. The power capacity of this UPS is 1200VA, which is enough to backup your essential devices for a considerable amount of time during power outages." },
