  "xiaomi-11t-pro-5g-moonlight-white-mobile-phone": { highlights: ["About this item", "The 5G enabled flagship Snapdragon 888 chipset is designed on a 5nm fab process and is paired with LPDDR5 RAM and UFS 3.1 storage to ensure ultra-smooth performance and seamless multitasking experience.", "The 6.67\" FHD+ true 10-bit AMOLED display has a 120 Hz refresh rate along with 480Hz touch sampling rate.", "The flaship 108MP HM2 sensor, 8MP Ultra-Wide sensor and 5MP TeleMacro sensor ensures flawless photography as well as Videography in all scenarios and lighting conditions.", "The dual symmetrical speakers with Sound by Harman Kardon, comes with Dolby Atmos certification that brings out richer audio experience.", "The phone comes with 120W HyperCharge technology that can fully charge the massive 5000mAh battery in 17 minutes"], specs: [["Brand", "Xiaomi"], ["Model", "11T Pro"], ["Colour", "Moonlight White"], ["RAM", "8GB"], ["Internal Storage", "256GB"], ["Operating System", "MIUI 12.5, Android 11"], ["Battery Capacity", "5000 mAh"], ["Selfie Camera", "16 MP"], ["Rear Camera", "108 MP, 8 MP, 5 MP"], ["Screen Size (Diagonal)", "16.94 cm (6.67 inch)"], ["Operating System Type", "Android"], ["5G", "Yes"], ["Quick Charge", "Yes"], ["In The Box", "Adapter, USB Type-C Cable, SIM Eject Tool, Protective Case Quick Start Guide, Warranty Card"]], overview: "Xiaomi 11T Pro, Power adapter, USB cable, Type C to 3.5mm converter, SIM eject tool, Warranty card, User guide, Clear soft case, Screen protector pre-applied on the phone" },
